(10447, 'Silden 100 mg 8 f.c. tabs', 'سيلدين 100مجم 8 قرص', '46', '66', 'Sildenafil', 'Eipico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '100 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
